# NanoAdwaita labwc theme.
#
# This theme exists mainly to ship the GNOME/Adwaita-style titlebar button icons
# that sit beside this file (close/iconify/max/max_toggled, active + inactive
# SVGs — full-colour, so labwc renders them as authored). labwc resolves the
# button images by theme name, hence the `<theme><name>NanoAdwaita</name>` in
# rc.xml and this directory living on XDG_DATA_DIRS as
#   <data-dir>/share/themes/NanoAdwaita/labwc/
#
# All colours and sizing (titlebar padding, button dimensions, hover) are set in
# /etc/xdg/labwc/themerc-override, which labwc loads *after* this file — keep the
# tunables there so the whole look stays editable in one place.
